{"tid":1709552,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"‎【和理塞】大隱隱於市，如何保護自己","createTime":"2019-11-12T02:12:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T07:46:12.000Z","uid":205733,"like":62,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"79a8c16e9ee2201090b5356d18bda4bdffd1bc46","tid":1709552,"uid":205733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T02:12:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大家良好市民來，梗係要好好保護自己，千祈唔好俾正義既警察叔叔拉錯好人呀</span></strong></span><br />\n- 唔好著黑衫，你係一個上班族，就算唔係都好，你係去見工，至少著smart casual<br />\n- 學生返學記得帶電腦參考書，你趕緊返學校上堂<br />\n- 睇病記得帶醫生紙<br />\n- 盡量迴避警察，少接觸，少拉錯好人<br />\n- 如果俾警察逗，記得態度良好，唔好挑機<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">&ldquo;自己係中立，D人阻住我返工返學，我都好憤怒，辛苦曬呀sir<br />\n不斷閙示威者，盡量唔透露身份證以外任何資料&rdquo;</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果差佬逗錯藍屍廢老唔知點算呢<br />\n大家記得做守法奉公既良好市民，唔好做犯法行爲！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"fce97c8033ed71ebd95db644a39ce56ac1af46f8","tid":1709552,"uid":205733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T02:12:58.000Z","msg":"大家小心"},{"pid":"a846344c5a8b40f5d15191e220495ad9998c6e73","tid":1709552,"uid":205733,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T02:18:29.000Z","msg":"班警察係單細胞生物，以爲所有野都可以暴力解決<br />\n同罷工一樣<br />\n合法/進取式/隱蔽的和理非行動，警察其實無能爲力<br />\n唔通警察用TG 捉人返工咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當然我唔鼓吹人去做啦"},{"pid":"5fcf44a7bdaa708c7b43b3572b2257fa7b237be4","tid":1709552,"uid":205733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T02:20:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"01760c0e24fca56bdafd421d1e492388342e0c69","tid":1709552,"uid":205733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T02:21:10.000Z","msg":"保護守法市民"},{"pid":"412becef3486ec5edc070d3ff41e954d76046a83","tid":1709552,"uid":18728,